  "detailed_description": "Looped is a short interactive story in which you solve mini-puzzles to progress a peaceful story about love, rockets, and time travel.<br><br>This is a story of a love-at-first-sight so powerful it creates a wormhole in time. From the end to the beginning and back again, you follow Him and Her and help them with tasks along their way.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/cb79130a5a89a110b9882741f94b80eb.poster.avif?t=1765221335\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/cb79130a5a89a110b9882741f94b80eb.webm?t=1765221335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/cb79130a5a89a110b9882741f94b80eb.mp4?t=1765221335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A black hole appears suddenly in a young woman’s living room. An unconscious man falls out. He opens his eyes and it’s love at first sight. Or is this the first sight?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/4fa49119cc5ade86ed58685f818b7240.webp?t=1765221335\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/4fa49119cc5ade86ed58685f818b7240.poster.avif?t=1765221335\" class=\"bb_img\" width=607 height=31 /></picture></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/0839b889d92c570f34020e253b9742ac.poster.avif?t=1765221335\" width=616 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/0839b889d92c570f34020e253b9742ac.webm?t=1765221335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/0839b889d92c570f34020e253b9742ac.mp4?t=1765221335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features<br>- A wordless story based on an award-winning short film<br>- Illustrated with beautiful hand-drawn 2D frame-by-frame animation<br>- Original soundtrack by United Sound<br>- Find the hidden Easter eggs<br><br><br>“Looped” is based on the award-winning short film of the same name, with the film based on the short story appearing in the book Ouvertyr och andra sagor för nästan vuxna written by Thomas Costa Freté in 2022.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/4fa49119cc5ade86ed58685f818b7240.webp?t=1765221335\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/4fa49119cc5ade86ed58685f818b7240.poster.avif?t=1765221335\" class=\"bb_img\" width=607 height=31 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/1b0d103be0d37b350ba2f89f4d4eab07.poster.avif?t=1765221335\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/1b0d103be0d37b350ba2f89f4d4eab07.webm?t=1765221335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/1b0d103be0d37b350ba2f89f4d4eab07.mp4?t=1765221335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/76f07cb0c293e9d8471563644b103e9b.poster.avif?t=1765221335\" width=617 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/76f07cb0c293e9d8471563644b103e9b.webm?t=1765221335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/1f93665970cc782a71ba87d63b5b932f.poster.avif?t=1765221335\" width=616 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/1f93665970cc782a71ba87d63b5b932f.webm?t=1765221335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/1f93665970cc782a71ba87d63b5b932f.mp4?t=1765221335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/4fa49119cc5ade86ed58685f818b7240.webp?t=1765221335\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/4fa49119cc5ade86ed58685f818b7240.poster.avif?t=1765221335\" class=\"bb_img\" width=607 height=31 /></picture></span>",
